href="jms-00BN.xml"
type="local"
addr="jms-00BN">event structure</fr:link> is called <fr:em>elementary</fr:em> when every finite set of events is <fr:link
href="jms-00BN.xml"
type="local"
addr="jms-00BN">consistent</fr:link>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree><fr:tree
xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml"
